# Platform — Hotsite Admin
# UC-027: Admin manages hotsite
# Guarded by ManagerRoleGuard — requires X-Actor-Role: MANAGER on every request.
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run seed
#   4. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get full hotsite content (includes unpublished state)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### Generate signed URL for a branding logo upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/signed-url
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileName": "logo.png",
  "contentType": "image/png",
  "purpose": "branding"
}

###

### Generate a private read-signed URL for a not-yet-promoted tmp/ image (TD22)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/read-signed-url
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tmp/{{tenantId}}/branding/019f420c-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/logo.png"
}

###

### Partial branding update (only colors changed)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branding": {
    "primaryColor": "#f97316",
    "secondaryColor": "#fff7ed"
  }
}

###

### Layout update — toggle a module's enabled flag
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "layout": [
    { "type": "HERO", "enabled": true, "data": { "variant": "centered", "title": "Bem-vindo", "ctaLabel": "Agendar agora", "ctaTarget": "booking" } },
    { "type": "SERVICE_LIST", "enabled": true, "data": { "showPrices": true, "showPoints": true, "layout": "grid" } },
    { "type": "GALLERY", "enabled": false, "data": { "images": [], "layout": "grid", "maxVisible": 6 } }
  ]
}

###

### SEO update — tenant-configured title and description for search results / social sharing
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seo": {
    "title": "Lavacar Estrela — Agendamento Online em São Paulo",
    "description": "Agende sua lavagem na Lavacar Estrela. Rápido, fácil e online."
  }
}

###

### Feature a booking's after-service photo on the hotsite gallery
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/gallery/feature-booking-photo
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001",
  "photoUrl": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/bookings/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/after-1.jpg"
}

###

### Delete a hotsite image from the public bucket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/delete
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/hotsite/branding/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/logo.png"
}

###

### Publish hotsite (requires at least one enabled module)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/publish
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### Unpublish hotsite
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/unpublish
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 400 — Invalid hex color
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branding": {
    "primaryColor": "notacolor"
  }
}

###

### 400 — Unknown layout module type
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "layout": [
    { "type": "UNKNOWN_MODULE", "enabled": true, "data": {} }
  ]
}

###

### 400 — hotsite-image-not-uploaded (logoUrl path not present in GCS)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branding": {
    "logoUrl": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/hotsite/branding/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/logo-not-uploaded.png"
  }
}

###

### 400 — Empty body (neither branding, layout, nor seo provided)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 400 — seo.title exceeds 70 characters
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seo": {
    "title": "Esse título é proposital e absurdamente longo para violar o limite máximo de setenta caracteres permitidos"
  }
}

###

### 400 — signed-url with invalid purpose
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/signed-url
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileName": "banner.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "purpose": "invalid-purpose"
}

###

### 400 — read-signed-url with a cross-tenant tmp/ path (TD22)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/read-signed-url
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tmp/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000099/branding/019f420c-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/logo.png"
}

###

### 400 — read-signed-url with a filePath outside the hotsite tmp/ shape (e.g. a booking tmp/
### upload — tmp/<tenantId>/<uuid>/<fileName>, missing the <purpose> segment) (TD22)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/read-signed-url
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tmp/{{tenantId}}/019f420c-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/logo.png"
}

###

### 404 — feature-booking-photo with unknown bookingId
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/gallery/feature-booking-photo
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000099",
  "photoUrl": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/bookings/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000099/after-1.jpg"
}

###

### 400 — feature-booking-photo with photoUrl not on the booking's before/after lists
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/gallery/feature-booking-photo
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001",
  "photoUrl": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/bookings/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/not-on-booking.jpg"
}

###

### 400 — Delete with a filePath belonging to another tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/delete
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002/hotsite/branding/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/logo.png"
}

###

### 400 — Delete with a filePath outside the tenants/<id>/hotsite/... shape
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/images/delete
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/bookings/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/after-1.jpg"
}

###

### 400 — Publish with no enabled modules
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/publish
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{managerId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: MANAGER

###

### 403 — STAFF role not allowed (ManagerRoleGuard rejects)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{staffId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: STAFF

###

### 403 — STAFF cannot feature a booking photo (ManagerRoleGuard rejects)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/hotsite/gallery/feature-booking-photo
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{staffId}}
X-Actor-Type: STAFF
X-Actor-Role: STAFF
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001",
  "photoUrl": "tenants/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001/bookings/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000001/after-1.jpg"
}
